zed for coalesced loads, reduced HBM round-trips, and better register allocation.', 'Conduct A/B latency races on a commodity GPU, comparing the default layout with our optimized layout.', 'Measure p50/p99 latency, throughput under batching, and energy per token.', 'Validate accuracy using standard benchmarks (e.g., ImageNet for vision transformers, WikiText for language models).'], 'Risk Factors and Limitations': ['The optimized layout may introduce additional complexity, potentially requiring more sophisticated kernel tuning.', 'The benefits may vary across different hardware architectures and GPU models.', 'The approach may not generalize well to all transformer variants, particularly those with non-standard attention mechanisms.']}
