      "Compare against BitDecoding and other state-of-the-art methods, reporting p50/p99 latency and tokens-per-second."
    ],
    "Risk Factors and Limitations": [
      "Complexity of implementing cache-aware reordering for diverse attention mechanisms.",
      "Potential overhead from dynamic reordering during inference.",
      "Compatibility with different GPU architectures and driver versions."
    ]
  }
}
